        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Take Your Shot Act</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of the Treasury to establish a national incentive program to award $1 million cash prizes to 100 eligible individuals who have received at least one COVID-19 vaccination. Prize money shall not be considered income for purposes of federal taxes.</p>]]>
        </text>
